&lt;li&gt;Be disciplined and have demonstrated experience in managing sales velocity and developing and nurturing multi level relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be insightful and inquisitive and be able to feed market feedback into development of new products and solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
