&lt;p&gt;This is an Engineering Manager role for someone who wants to stay close to hard technical and data problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nuitée is hiring an Engineering Manager to own the mapping platform that turns messy global hotel supply into accurate, trusted, sellable inventory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll lead a business-critical domain where matching, deduplication, content enrichment, automation, and ML directly affect whether hotel inventory can be searched, trusted, booked, and sold.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every supplier describes the hotel world differently. The same hotel can appear under different IDs. Room types can be named and structured differently. Content can be incomplete, duplicated, mismatched, or attached to the wrong hotel or room.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cupid is our internal mapping platform. It covers hotel mapping, room mapping, content mapping, and the operational workflows that keep inventory quality high at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your role is to lead the team behind it, modernise the systems and workflows, and build a clearer operating model across engineering, data/ML, and mapping operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A good way to think of it is: you turn fragmented supplier data into reliable inventory that customers can search, trust, book, and sell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What makes it interesting for you&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You own a hard, specific domain at the core of hotel inventory quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You stay close to technical decisions, architecture, data flows, and tradeoffs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You work on production ML problems around matching, classification, enrichment, automation, and data quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You modernise a mature platform with real room to improve the systems, workflows, and team structure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your work connects directly to conversion, supply quality, customer experience, and revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-ownership role with high expectations, and it comes with meaningful equity in the company. Nuitée was already profitable before raising a $48M Series A led by Accel, and has grown 10x since 2022. If you help build the next phase of Nuitée, we want you to share meaningfully in the value you create.&lt;/p&gt;
